        subsystem - The subsystem to run the path gotten from the Jetson on.

        poseEstimator - The object to get robot pose from.
        x - The absolute X position, in feet, for the robot to go to. Can be null to set pose using setters.
        y - The absolute Y position, in feet, for the robot to go to. Can be null to set pose using setters.

        maxVel - The maximum velocity, in units/second.
        maxAccel - The maximum acceleration, in units/(second^2)
        maxJerk - The maximum jerk, in units/(second^3)
        deltaTime - The time between setpoints in the profile, in seconds.
